fbc","tid":984753,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94c65b2a8710d875e40ead2f03dccf1f4aed8a8","tid":984753,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:23:31.000Z","msg":"簽完之後下一步係咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"一直以嚟藝發局都未被赤化，但近排出現咗啲波折，有留意新聞或者圈內人應該都feel 到...呢個促請有試探性質，從而決定點應對呢個半官方組織。(聯署愈多人咁當然愈好傾) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n若果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲有其他方案嘅不過就係藝發局之外嘅事所以唔嚮呢度講嘞。"},{"pid":"4357afe8e032322be8934f51942abb9e3b8a5b93","tid":984753,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T04:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04864463da0a43f2f08ba18e1b3ba0271e5a6d8d","tid":984753,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}